Who are the users of the software?
- the users would be business owners who would be interested in implementing a pos system.
What is the purpose of the software?
- the purpose of the software is to make check out for customers easy. 
Where and when will the software be used?
- the software would be used at shops to make it convenient for the customers to get their order.
How does the software work?
- the software works by asking users for their order then letting them modify it and printing out a receipt at the end of it. 
Why would anyone want to use the software over existing processes?
- this software specifically targets boba shop owners. however, it could be implemented in any type of business who
needs a POS system. 
